      "description": "<p>Arremesso, Invocação</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Com um sibilo e movimento do braço invoca um espírito de serpente que dá um bote a partir de seu braço.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço:</span> 7.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1 ação.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 5/10m.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 7+ESP/2.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> Penetrante, se causar ao menos 1 de dano o alvo recebe [12+COG</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">+</span>4<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family:'MS Mincho';mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">Ⓐ</span>] de dano Biológico: Tóxico e Peste (1).</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Pré-requisitos:</span> <em>Espírito da presa</em> e Druidismo N6.</p>",
